text: Hello NAMESLOTU!
I am an Amazon representative.
I understand that you have recently purchased something online.
Hi!
I ordered a heater on Amazon and it has not come in yet.
"I apologize for the inconvenience, and I would be happy to fix that for you."
Okay
would you please confirm the name/type of heater you purchased?
The Heatblaster 500 - the black portable one
"Perfect, thanks."
I am checking my records.
Could you please confirm your credit card number?
"Actually, it was the Digital Ceramic Tower Heater with Remote."
I got it confused.
No problem.
Are you still missing the Digital Ceramic Tower Heater?
"Yes, it still has not arrived."
"Ok, thanks."
I am checking my records.
Could you confirm your credit card number?
I purchased it on prime so that I could get it before the blizzard.
"Ok, thanks."
"For me to check your records, I need your credit card number on file."
Can you just look up my purchased via my account?
Let me check with my manager.
Can I have your full name and address?
My name is NAMESLOTU.
My address is linked to my account as well.
I apologize I cannot access your account without your address and credit card number.
"Well, before I follow through with the purchase."
Is it a good heater?
"I have not used the heater myself, but I understand that it has very high ratings."
I saw that too.
Does it require an outlet or is it battery-operated?
"I apologize, as an Amazon account representative, I do not have that information."
I don't have time to return it now that it's late so I'm being selective
I thought it had not been delivered yet.
It has not been delivered but I need to know it's right.
What is your name again?
